OL,7,FWhile a new building was finally
OL,8,Fopened in September following several
OL,9,Fdelays, there is still unresolved
OL,10,Fconstruction work meaning the project
OL,11,Fremains incomplete.
OL,13,FISG was awarded the contract for the
OL,14,F#21 million project which started in
OL,15,F2021.
OL,17,FThe company tried to find a buyer but
OL,18,Ffailed to secure a suitable rescue
OL,19,Fdeal, meaning 2,400 workers now face
OL,20,Flosing their jobs.
