OL,7,FISG is working on 69 central
OL,8,Fgovernment projects worth over #1
OL,9,Fbillion, including prison developments
OL,10,Fwhile also being contracted to build
OL,11,Fpolice and fire stations, schools and
OL,12,Foffices.
OL,14,FIn January 2024, when Governors sent
OL,15,Fin their own surveyor to Woodlands
OL,16,FMeed, a number of problems were
OL,17,Fidentified.
