OL,3,CBuilding saga continues for special
OL,4,Cneeds pupils in Sussex after ISG
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FThese included unfinished floors,
OL,8,Fceilings which are too low to
OL,9,Faccommodate wheelchair hoists, gaps in
OL,10,Fthe brickwork, an atrium with no rail
OL,11,Fto stop children falling onto concrete
OL,12,Fand hygiene rooms where floors are too
OL,13,Fhigh for water to flow away into the
OL,14,Fgulley.
OL,16,FWest Sussex County Council,
OL,17,Fresponsible for contracting ISG,
OL,18,Fconfirmed a second phase of works at
OL,19,Fthe site are currently suspended.
