OL,3,CBuilding saga continues for special
OL,4,Cneeds pupils in Sussex after ISG
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FThe authority said in a statement, "We
OL,8,Fare extremely disappointed at this
OL,9,Fnews and had no prior warning that
OL,10,Fthis was about to happen.
OL,12,F"We will be working with the college
OL,13,Fand the administrators of ISG, when
OL,14,Fappointed, to ensure the work is
OL,15,Fcompleted with as little disruption to
OL,16,Fpupils and staff at the college.
OL,18,F"Once an administrator has been
OL,19,Fappointed, we will seek to complete
OL,20,Fthe works as soon as possible, which
OL,21,Fmay be with another contractor.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
